This mutator allows you to configure:

- Max Dmg
- Impact Dmg ( For Rocket Launchers / Demo Weapons )
- Magazine Size
- Ammo Cost
- Cost
- Weight
- HeadShot multiplier
- Reload Speed
- Reload Animation Speed
- Fire Rate
- Fire Rate Animation speed


Of all weapons. Custom or Official!

- [url=https://github.com/Vel-San/KF-WeaponStatConfig/commits/master]Track My Progress Here[/url]

[H1][b][u]Notes[/u][/b][/H1]

- As of [b]v1.3[/b], this mutator is [b]WHITELISTED[/b]
- This is a server-side mutator, players do not have to download anything! (You don't have to compress and host it)

[H1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/H1]

- 3

[H1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- \System\KFWeaponStatConfig.u
- \System\KFWeaponStatConfig.ucl
- \System\KFWeaponStatConfig.ini

[H1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/H1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list
4- Before you start your server, navigate to your directory and edit the configuration file. Add/Remove whatever weapon you want. Follow instructions in the config file to understand what each value does.

Sample config can be as the following:

[code]
[KFWeaponStatConfig.KFWeaponStatConfig]
bDebug=True
# FireAnime & ReloadAnime: + To Increase | Low or High Values might break the Animations or make it slow-mo, increase/decrease gradually
# FireRate & ReloadRate: - To Increase | Low or High Values might break fFireRate or make it slow-mo, increase/decrease gradually
# MagCapacity, ReloadRate & ReloadAnimRate are ignored for MeleeWeapons
# ImpactDamage is only for weapons with Impact such as Rocket Laucnhers (e.g. Demo Weapons)
# This list will 'Edit' the weapon stats
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.Single",iMagCapacity=50,iDamageMax=3000,iWeight=0,iCost=0,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=0.175,fFireAnimRate=1.5,fReloadRate=2.0,fReloadAnimRate=2.0)
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.M99SniperRifle",iMagCapacity=10,iDamageMax=5000,iWeight=2,iCost=5,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=1,fFireAnimRate=1.0,fReloadRate=1,fReloadAnimRate=2.5)
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.KrissMMedicGun",iMagCapacity=100,iDamageMax=3000,iWeight=2,iCost=5,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=0.06,fFireAnimRate=1,fReloadRate=1.5,fReloadAnimRate=2.5)
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.NeonKrissMMedicGun",iMagCapacity=100,iDamageMax=3000,iWeight=2,iCost=5,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=0.06,fFireAnimRate=1,fReloadRate=1.5,fReloadAnimRate=2.5)
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.MP5MMedicGun",iMagCapacity=100,iDamageMax=3000,iWeight=2,iCost=5,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=0.08,fFireAnimRate=1,fReloadRate=1.5,fReloadAnimRate=2.7)
Weapon=(sWeaponClassName="KFMod.M32GrenadeLauncher",iMagCapacity=35,iDamageMax=3000,iWeight=2,iCost=5,iImpactDamage=0,fHeadShotDamageMult=2.0,fFireRate=0.33,fFireAnimRate=1.0,fReloadRate=1.0,fReloadAnimRate=1.8)



[KFWeaponStatConfig.Helper]
# This list is to 'Print' default stats for a weapon
# If bDebug=True --> Stats will be printed in your server.log (or Killingfloor.log)
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.BlowerThrower"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.BoomStick"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.Bullpup"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.CamoM32GrenadeLauncher"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.CamoM4AssaultRifle"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.CamoMP5MMedicGun"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.CamoShotgun"
PrintStatsFor="KFMod.Chainsaw"
[/code]

